RelatedSentence: The Americas was the second largest destination , accounting for of about 63,014 tons of rice exports ( equivalent to about 35 % of total rice exports in May 2014 ) .

Vietnam also exported 27,358 tons of rice to the Africa , about 6,477 tons of rice to Europe , about 1,444 tons of rice to the Middle East , and about 134 tons of rice to Australia so far in May 2014 .
